name: Classic Monogram Necklace
description:
What better gift to give your loved ones personalized jewelry! 

One of the hottest trends in personalized jewelry, this monogram necklace is a great way to show off your own style and uniqueness. You can choose up to three initials to create this picture perfect monogram piece.

•MATERIAL: 18K Gold Plating over 0.925 Sterling Silver

•Chain style: 18k Gold Plated Sterling Silver Rollo Chain
  (NOTE: The mini monogram chain comes in  bead style)

•Chain length:	14"(CHILD),16",18",20",22"
